<div class="feature-panel feature-panel--statistics">
  <div class="feature-panel__inner">
    <h3 class=feature-panel__title>Statistics</h3>
    <div class="feature-panel__shapes">
      <div class="feature-shape feature-shape--primary"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-panel__text">
      <p>
        Research shows that alcohol problems are highly recoverable: in one large longitudinal study,
        <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC7018515/"
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener"
           class="alcohol-studies__link">
          87% of people recovered from their first alcohol use disorder episode
        </a>
        by age 30, even though some experienced later recurrences. In separate work, researchers found that
        <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC12413015/"
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener"
           class="alcohol-studies__link">
          each one‑point increase in “happiness with recovery”
        </a>
        was linked with being more likely to be abstinent and to complete treatment. Trials of
        <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC12346788/"
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener"
           class="alcohol-studies__link">
          positive psychology and journaling exercises in addiction treatment
        </a>
        report good feasibility and improvements in wellbeing and recovery resources.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-panel__image-inner">
    <div class="feature-panel__shapes">
      <div class="feature-shape feature-shape--secondary"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-panel__image">
      <%= image_tag "",
            alt: "Statistics and charts",
            class: "feature-panel-image" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
